3	occupation	manufacturing	0	Business/intermediate purchases are exempt and manufacturers face generic seller rules; no occupation-specific effect.	1.00	{"0": 3}
3	occupation	agriculture	0	Findings mention family farms and estate taxes, but the effect on farmers mirrors that of any business owner rather than being agriculture-trait-dependent.	0.67	{"0": 2, "1": 1}
