3	occupation	public_sector_first_responders	1	The bill makes state governments the primary administrators/collectors of the national sales tax and treats governments as taxable employers, directly affecting state revenue-agency and government workers.	0.67	{"0": 1, "1": 2}
3	occupation	professional_office	1	Abolishing the IRS and repealing the income, payroll, and estate taxes directly transforms the work of tax accountants, preparers, and tax attorneys within this white-collar category, and professional services become taxable.	1.00	{"1": 3}
3	occupation	retail_service	2	The bill makes sellers of goods and services the front-line collectors and remitters of the national sales tax (with an administration credit), directly imposing new operational duties on retail, hospitality, food, and personal-service businesses selling to final consumers.	0.67	{"1": 1, "2": 2}
