3	employment_status	employee	2	The bill repeals the income tax and payroll (FICA) withholding that directly govern employees' wages and take-home pay, and defines rules for wages paid by taxable employers. Employees are explicit, direct subjects of the repealed withholding regime and the new consumption-based system.	1.00	{"2": 3}
3	employment_status	self_employed_owner	2	Self-employment taxes are explicitly repealed, and business owners/sellers are made directly responsible for collecting and remitting the national sales tax, with business-purchase exemptions, administration credits, and estate/gift tax repeal for family businesses. They are direct subjects of multiple provisions firsthand.	1.00	{"2": 3}
